data_table.description: MESA Classic Aortic Valvular Calcium Dataset: This dataset consist of aortic valvular calcium CT phenotype variables collected during MESA Classic Exams 1-3. The dataset includes measurements of calcium in the aortic valve, mitral valve, aortic wall, aortic valve ring, and ascending and descending thoracic aorta.
